In this lab. exercise you need to provide user authentication. You should provide registration, user login and management of user login information.

User registration
You need to create a system for user registration, users should be able to register on your application using necessary information such as username, email and secure password.

User login
Once the users are registered, they should be able to log in to the system, so you should implement a user login system that checks the entered data and compares it with the data you saved during registration.

Managing login information
User data is crucial, you need to store and manage it securely, you must ensure the confidentiality and integrity of user data.
